{"tid":2029292,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"受訪回應制裁措施   華為高層：美國將會損失慘重","createTime":"2020-05-22T07:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T08:11:30.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ca7ca97239344c9ec1c3ea69e1dad35c37b9eaab","tid":2029292,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T07:24:14.000Z","msg":"受訪回應制裁措施   華為高層：美國將會損失慘重<br />\n虎仔 / 馬日山(uniqlo) 2020-05-22 11:55<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普早前簽署行政命令，將國家緊急狀態延長一年，被納入實體清單的華為繼續被封殺。及後美國政府還進一步「加辣」，使用美國技術或器材的廠商被限制不可向華為供應晶片。華為美國的高層日前接受傳媒訪問，卻表示禁令影響美國人比較多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2020-05/22/215886/uniqlo_1_ea60bd9d5cf0328d75005a489ee2c2fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2020-05%2F22%2F215886%2Funiqlo_1_ea60bd9d5cf0328d75005a489ee2c2fc.jpg&h=ae0db1a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在接受彭博通訊社訪問時，華為美國的首席安全主管 Andy Purdy 表示，美國政府的制裁措施對美國人傷害遠多於華為。Purdy 又表示華為始終會恢復過來，並且適應全新的環境，但措施影響全球業界，很多美國人將會因此而失業。他表示針對華為的措施進一步擴張，只會逼使華為全面在中國進行採購，讓美國和其他國家的公司失去生意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該名華為高層表示當公司長遠能夠獨立，毋須再需要依賴美國科技之後，就不會走回頭路，而其他大陸企業亦會仿效，最終對美國的競爭力構成打擊，甚至有可能會擴散到電訊以外的其他行業。Andy Purdy 又提到，他對中國政府可能作出的反制措施，例如制裁 Apple 等美國科技公司感到憂慮，這樣可能會引發新一輪更激烈的貿易戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4546/215886/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4546%2F215886%2F1%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSrJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=c061e5dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4546/215886/1/</a>"},{"pid":"b5378c677b55e68b1fcca7a1eea711fd6dd01efd","tid":2029292,"uid":279311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T07:25:59.000Z","msg":"遺言<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baba532db82f863930373127ad7b52e130acd2d5","tid":2029292,"uid":281306,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T07:26:52.000Z","msg":"又廢up<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4d02863411fb6732ab2058374fc9e5c50bacbb","tid":2029292,"uid":168297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T07:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nBNsDxP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnBNsDxP.jpg&h=f8b72f5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ab66265106711791e7ec7f3953eed36110bca41","tid":2029292,"uid":310446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T07:39:13.000Z","msg":"華為高層? Sorry你邊位呀?"},{"pid":"b85092d956d9eedcddde73a99cda5b3559f1c49f","tid":2029292,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:04:23.000Z","msg":"連登手機台屎為5毛契弟唔該回應下"},{"pid":"d784ceaa66b51db65ef3ad8357601de2bb371b18","tid":2029292,"uid":7609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:06:55.000Z","msg":"算鳩數啦"},{"pid":"67aa5e66df2a4ffddb2d12d3db412bc6074c06eb","tid":2029292,"uid":345137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:11:30.000Z","msg":"被全世界禁售晶片制裁, 華為或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}